FoodEstablishment.name: hasMenu
FoodEstablishment.desc: Either the actual menu as a structured representation, as text, or a URL of the menu.

FoodEstablishment.name: menu
FoodEstablishment.desc: Either the actual menu as a structured representation, as text, or a URL of the menu.

FoodEstablishment.name: starRating
FoodEstablishment.desc: An official rating for a lodging business or food establishment, e.g. from national associations or standards bodies. Use the author property to indicate the rating organization, e.g. as an Organization with name such as (e.g. HOTREC, DEHOGA, WHR, or Hotelstars).

FoodEstablishment.name: acceptsReservations
FoodEstablishment.desc: Indicates whether a FoodEstablishment accepts reservations. Values can be Boolean, an URL at which reservations can be made or (for backwards compatibility) the strings Yes or No.
